[{"text": "(Singing)", "start": 17.26, "duration": 2.968}, {"text": "(Singing ends)", "start": 33.083, "duration": 1.341}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 138.171, "duration": 6.658}, {"text": "Pep Rosenfeld: Folks,\nyou've just met Claron McFadden.", "start": 146.779, "duration": 3.008}, {"text": "She is a world-class soprano singer", "start": 149.811, "duration": 2.587}, {"text": "who studied in Rochester, New York.", "start": 152.422, "duration": 1.814}, {"text": "Her celebrated operatic roles\nare numerous and varied.", "start": 154.938, "duration": 3.297}, {"text": "In August 2007, Claron was awarded\nthe Amsterdam Prize for the Arts,", "start": 158.649, "duration": 5.571}, {"text": "winning praise for her brilliance,", "start": 164.244, "duration": 1.815}, {"text": "her amazing and extensively\nwide repertoire", "start": 166.083, "duration": 3.406}, {"text": "and her vivid stage personality.", "start": 169.513, "duration": 1.723}, {"text": "Please welcome Claron McFadden.", "start": 171.704, "duration": 1.946}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 173.674, "duration": 6.92}, {"text": "Claron McFadden: The human voice:", "start": 184.66, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "mysterious, spontaneous, primal.", "start": 187.334, "duration": 3.773}, {"text": "For me, the human voice is the vessel\non which all emotions travel --", "start": 193.053, "duration": 4.937}, {"text": "except, perhaps, jealousy.", "start": 198.014, "duration": 1.913}, {"text": "And the breath,", "start": 201.84, "duration": 1.475}, {"text": "the breath is the captain of that vessel.", "start": 203.339, "duration": 2.156}, {"text": "A child is born,", "start": 207.591, "duration": 1.562}, {"text": "takes its first breath --", "start": 210.558, "duration": 1.643}, {"text": "(Inhales)", "start": 212.863, "duration": 3.913}, {"text": "Whah!", "start": 218.01, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "And we behold the wondrous beauty", "start": 220.531, "duration": 3.066}, {"text": "of vocal expression --", "start": 224.954, "duration": 1.484}, {"text": "mysterious, spontaneous", "start": 227.188, "duration": 2.623}, {"text": "and primal.", "start": 230.899, "duration": 1.151}, {"text": "A few years ago, I did\na meditation retreat in Thailand.", "start": 233.923, "duration": 3.142}, {"text": "I wanted a place", "start": 237.089, "duration": 1.453}, {"text": "where I would have total silence\nand total solitude.", "start": 239.279, "duration": 3.957}, {"text": "I spent two weeks at this retreat", "start": 243.988, "duration": 2.607}, {"text": "in my own little hut --", "start": 246.619, "duration": 1.714}, {"text": "no music, no nothing -- sounds of nature,", "start": 248.357, "duration": 2.809}, {"text": "trying to find the essence\nof concentration,", "start": 252.214, "duration": 3.539}, {"text": "being in the moment.", "start": 255.777, "duration": 1.458}, {"text": "On my last day,", "start": 257.937, "duration": 1.857}, {"text": "the woman who looked after the place,", "start": 259.818, "duration": 2.119}, {"text": "she came and we spoke for a minute,", "start": 262.675, "duration": 2.176}, {"text": "and then she said to me,", "start": 264.875, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "\"Would you sing something for me?\"", "start": 267.581, "duration": 1.655}, {"text": "And I thought, but this is a place\nof total quiet and silence.", "start": 269.915, "duration": 3.277}, {"text": "I can't make noise.", "start": 273.216, "duration": 1.531}, {"text": "She said, \"Please, sing for me.\"", "start": 275.81, "duration": 2.45}, {"text": "So I closed my eyes,", "start": 279.553, "duration": 1.683}, {"text": "I took breath", "start": 282.18, "duration": 1.277}, {"text": "and the first thing that came up and out", "start": 285.1, "duration": 2.5}, {"text": "was \"Summertime,\"", "start": 288.465, "duration": 1.397}, {"text": "Porgy and Bess.", "start": 291.037, "duration": 1.198}, {"text": "(Singing) Summertime\nand the livin' is easy.", "start": 292.259, "duration": 4.143}, {"text": "Fish are jumpin' and the cotton is high.", "start": 297.632, "duration": 3.142}, {"text": "Oh, your daddy's rich\nand your ma is good-lookin'.", "start": 300.798, "duration": 3.985}, {"text": "So hush little baby,", "start": 304.807, "duration": 1.59}, {"text": "don't you cry.", "start": 306.421, "duration": 2.425}, {"text": "And I opened my eyes,", "start": 310.103, "duration": 1.711}, {"text": "and I saw that she had her eyes closed.", "start": 312.473, "duration": 2.763}, {"text": "And after a moment, she opened her eyes", "start": 316.001, "duration": 2.103}, {"text": "and she looked at me and she said,", "start": 318.128, "duration": 1.658}, {"text": "\"It's like meditation.\"", "start": 321.025, "duration": 1.637}, {"text": "And in that moment I understood", "start": 323.765, "duration": 2.222}, {"text": "that everything I had gone\nto Thailand to look for,", "start": 326.011, "duration": 3.412}, {"text": "to search for,", "start": 329.447, "duration": 1.586}, {"text": "I had it already in my singing --", "start": 331.057, "duration": 2.395}, {"text": "the calm, but alertness,", "start": 334.866, "duration": 2.953}, {"text": "the focus, but awareness,", "start": 338.66, "duration": 2.493}, {"text": "and being totally in the moment.", "start": 341.804, "duration": 2.809}, {"text": "When you're totally in the moment --", "start": 346.295, "duration": 1.746}, {"text": "when I'm totally in the moment,", "start": 348.065, "duration": 1.499}, {"text": "the vessel of expression is open.", "start": 349.588, "duration": 2.205}, {"text": "The emotions can flow from me", "start": 351.817, "duration": 2.572}, {"text": "to you", "start": 354.413, "duration": 1.173}, {"text": "and back.", "start": 355.61, "duration": 1.196}, {"text": "It's an extremely profound experience.", "start": 357.817, "duration": 1.889}, {"text": "There's a piece by a composer,", "start": 362.047, "duration": 2.35}, {"text": "an American composer called John Cage.", "start": 364.421, "duration": 2.598}, {"text": "It's called \"Aria.\"", "start": 367.043, "duration": 1.58}, {"text": "It was written for an amazing singer\ncalled Cathy Berberian.", "start": 368.647, "duration": 4.589}, {"text": "And the thing about this piece\nthat's so special --", "start": 373.752, "duration": 2.484}, {"text": "if you see it behind me --", "start": 376.942, "duration": 1.294}, {"text": "it's not notated in any way.", "start": 379.267, "duration": 2.174}, {"text": "No notes, no flats, no sharps.", "start": 382.669, "duration": 2.691}, {"text": "But it's a kind of structure.", "start": 386.058, "duration": 1.746}, {"text": "And the singer, within this structure,", "start": 388.431, "duration": 2.46}, {"text": "has total freedom\nto be creative, spontaneous.", "start": 390.915, "duration": 4.02}, {"text": "For example,", "start": 395.538, "duration": 1.151}, {"text": "there are different colors", "start": 397.832, "duration": 1.547}, {"text": "and each color gets\na different type of singing --", "start": 399.403, "duration": 3.952}, {"text": "pop, country and western, opera, jazz --", "start": 403.379, "duration": 3.889}, {"text": "and you just have\nto be consistent with that color.", "start": 407.292, "duration": 3.127}, {"text": "You see there are different lines.", "start": 411.61, "duration": 1.849}, {"text": "You choose in your own tempo\nin your own way", "start": 413.998, "duration": 2.207}, {"text": "to follow the line,", "start": 416.229, "duration": 1.253}, {"text": "but you must respect it,", "start": 417.506, "duration": 1.408}, {"text": "more or less.", "start": 419.726, "duration": 1.157}, {"text": "And these little dots,", "start": 421.391, "duration": 1.484}, {"text": "these represent a sort of sound", "start": 423.906, "duration": 3.418}, {"text": "that's not a vocal, not a lyrical way", "start": 428.459, "duration": 2.777}, {"text": "of expressing the voice.", "start": 431.26, "duration": 2.207}, {"text": "Using the body -- it could be sneezing,", "start": 433.491, "duration": 2.061}, {"text": "it could be coughing, animals --", "start": 435.576, "duration": 1.579}, {"text": "(Audience member coughs)", "start": 437.179, "duration": 1.595}, {"text": "Exactly. (Laughter)", "start": 438.798, "duration": 1.292}, {"text": "Clapping, whatever.", "start": 440.114, "duration": 1.653}, {"text": "And there's different text.", "start": 443.138, "duration": 1.967}, {"text": "There's Armenian, Russian,\nFrench, English, Italian.", "start": 445.129, "duration": 3.735}, {"text": "So within this structure, one is free.", "start": 449.459, "duration": 2.508}, {"text": "To me, this piece is an ode to the voice,", "start": 452.945, "duration": 2.603}, {"text": "because it's mysterious, as we can see.", "start": 456.992, "duration": 2.548}, {"text": "It's quite spontaneous.", "start": 461.413, "duration": 1.642}, {"text": "And it's primal.", "start": 465.811, "duration": 1.343}, {"text": "So I would like to share\nthis piece with you,", "start": 467.765, "duration": 2.19}, {"text": "It's \"Aria,\" of John Cage.", "start": 469.979, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "(Singing in various languages)", "start": 479.528, "duration": 1.453}, {"text": "Hampart-zoum", "start": 481.005, "duration": 4.452}, {"text": "Dirouhi", "start": 486.704, "duration": 1.496}, {"text": "Di questa Terra", "start": 488.224, "duration": 1.729}, {"text": "Naprasno", "start": 490.605, "duration": 3.404}, {"text": "Conscience et", "start": 494.033, "duration": 2.143}, {"text": "(Barks)", "start": 496.2, "duration": 1.213}, {"text": "(Singing) Arise", "start": 498.581, "duration": 6.976}, {"text": "Tsk, tsk, tsk.", "start": 505.991, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "(Singing)", "start": 508.761, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "Vidiel\u2019a", "start": 509.919, "duration": 1.934}, {"text": "facilmente", "start": 511.877, "duration": 2.468}, {"text": "E io sono per te", "start": 514.369, "duration": 4.381}, {"text": "(Robotic voice) No other way", "start": 519.123, "duration": 1.571}, {"text": "Dans l'espace, so help", "start": 520.718, "duration": 2.265}, {"text": "(Singing)", "start": 524.047, "duration": 1.135}, {"text": "Si juste", "start": 525.206, "duration": 3.142}, {"text": "Dvidz\u00e9nya bistri", "start": 528.372, "duration": 4.771}, {"text": "(Claps)", "start": 535.151, "duration": 1.396}, {"text": "(Singing)", "start": 537.183, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "On pekr\u00e1sen", "start": 538.341, "duration": 1.659}, {"text": "idyot a k u", "start": 540.024, "duration": 4.738}, {"text": "O a k ho a", "start": 544.786, "duration": 4.101}, {"text": "Sivayoot eternal loosin", "start": 550.237, "duration": 4.618}, {"text": "(Sneezes)", "start": 556.737, "duration": 2.944}, {"text": "(Laughs)", "start": 561.8, "duration": 1.278}, {"text": "Shh!", "start": 563.102, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "(Singing)", "start": 567.761, "duration": 1.126}, {"text": "Gloobino\u00ed pi\u00f9 chiara", "start": 568.911, "duration": 2.27}, {"text": "Si ceci est cela cela est ceci", "start": 573.514, "duration": 5.592}, {"text": "Totalmente soi whom they sought to slay", "start": 582.233, "duration": 5.117}, {"text": "To have the fruits gloire", "start": 588.711, "duration": 3.599}, {"text": "J\u2019\u00e9coute ...", "start": 593.175, "duration": 2.54}, {"text": "\u00c0 la vie\u2026", "start": 595.739, "duration": 1.872}, {"text": "Leggermente sn\u00e9dznoi", "start": 598.263, "duration": 4.546}, {"text": "Coo coo", "start": 605.373, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "P k t d", "start": 607.293, "duration": 3.421}, {"text": "Banalit\u00e9", "start": 610.738, "duration": 2.484}, {"text": "K o e", "start": 613.246, "duration": 3.065}, {"text": "(Makes the sound of a kiss)", "start": 617.343, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "(Singing)", "start": 620.994, "duration": 1.151}, {"text": "In armonia", "start": 622.169, "duration": 6.988}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 632.529, "duration": 6.92}]